io.github.mrblobman.spigotcommandlib

Class FragmentExecutionContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.mrblobman.spigotcommandlib.FragmentExecutionContext

  • public class FragmentExecutionContext
extends java.lang.Object
    Used to store state information that will be carried through fragment handlers. (See: FragmentedCommandHandle). The default implementation just handles state but registration may be on a class that extends this base.
